    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thank you for continuing to write. I love to see new posts on how you are doing. Love to hear about June. I have cooked more reading your book and blog and still hunger for more recipes and recommendations. Glad you are doing well and making your house your own. I know the feeling. Thank you and continue to write. I am out here excited for your posts.</p>
    </div>

